{"tid":2273162,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電視上月平均每日訂單量按年升83%","createTime":"2020-11-05T13:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T13:50:47.000Z","uid":29675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cb27f34a4b1bae987d5a796a92e09a4181e8a5a5","tid":2273162,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:50:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558556-20201105.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558556-20201105.htm&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8hR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=c3ceaac3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558556-20201105.htm&h=17dd16e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558556-20201105.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港電視公布，10月平均每日訂單數量按年升近83%，按月升近8%，平均訂單值465元，按年升2%，按月跌3.7%；每日訂單交易額1650萬元，按年升逾85%，按月升3.8%，每月訂單交易額5.13億元，按年升86%，按月升逾7%。"}]}